{{Infobox person | name = Mikel Ruffinelli | birth_name = Mikel Ruffinelli | birth_date = {{birth year and age|1972}} | birth_place = [[Los Angeles]] | residence = [[Los Angeles]] | nationality = [[United States|American]] | citizenship = [[United States|American]] | education = | occupation = Model/Housewife | known_for = Widest Hip (8ft) | height = {{height|m=1.62}} | weight = {{convert|420|lb}} | spouse = {{marriage|Reggie Brooks|2002}} | children = 4 }}
'''Mikel Ruffinelli''' (born 1972) is an American woman who currently holds the record of widest hip in the world,<ref>{{cite news|last=Griffo|first=Megan|title=Mikel Ruffinelli Sets World Record For Largest Hips|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/01/22/mikel-ruffinelli-worlds-largest-hips_n_2526338.html|accessdate=31 March 2013|newspaper=Huffington Post|date=22 January 2013}}</ref> according to the World Record Academy.<ref>{{cite web|title=Largest hips: Mikel Ruffinelli sets world record (VIDEO)|url=http://www.worldrecordacademy.com/human/largest_hips_Mikel_Ruffinelli_breaks_Guinness_world_record_213209.html|work=World Record Academy|accessdate=31 March 2013|date=January 21, 2013}}</ref> Her weight is more than {{convert|420|lb|kg}} and her hips measures an unusual {{convert|8|ft|m}} in circumference, although her waist is only {{convert|3|ft|4|in|cm}}. She is 5 feet 4 inches tall.
==Early life, marriage and pregnancy==
Mikel was a normal-sized young woman and in her early 20s weighed an above average {{convert|13|st|lb}}.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/news/4753600/woman-who-measures-over-8ft-around-middle.html|title=World's biggest hips: woman who measures over 8ft around middle |work= The Sun|author=Harry Haydon|date=20 January 2013 }}</ref> But at 22, she put on {{convert|4|st|lb}} after having first child Andrew. After daughters Destynee, Autumn, and Justyce followed, her weight and hips ballooned further.
She eats an average 5,000 calories a day.
Possibly this extraordinary fat tissue accumulation turns out to be an advanced stage of a medical condition called [[lipedema]].
